# Push ONLY the Apps Script source to the GAS project.
# Ignore everything first, then allow-list the real GAS files.
# Without this, clasp would try to push docs/*.html (the static OSS landing +
# demo) as HtmlService files and pollute the project.
**/**

!appsscript.json
!Code.gs
!Setup.gs
!index.html
!style.html
!script.html
!i18n.html
